## 9. File-by-File Explanation

### How All Components Connect

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                         main.ts                             │
│  Creates Winston logger BEFORE app boots.                   │
│  Passes it to NestFactory.create() for bootstrap logging.   │
└──────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘
                           │ imports
┌──────────────────────────▼──────────────────────────────────┐
│                      app.module.ts                           │
│  WinstonModule.forRoot() → makes logger available via DI    │
│  HealthModule → registers health endpoints                  │
│  APP_FILTER → GlobalExceptionFilter (uses Winston via DI)   │
│  configure() → applies RequestLoggerMiddleware              │
└───┬──────────────┬──────────────┬───────────────────────────┘
    │              │              │
    ▼              ▼              ▼
┌────────┐  ┌───────────┐  ┌──────────────┐
│Request │  │ Global    │  │   Health     │
│Logger  │  │ Exception │  │   Module     │
│Middle- │  │ Filter    │  │              │
│ware   │  │           │  │ Controller + │
│        │  │ @Inject   │  │ Prisma       │
│@Inject │  │ Winston   │  │ Health       │
│Winston │  │           │  │ Indicator    │
└────────┘  └───────────┘  └──────────────┘
```

| File | Role | Key Design Decision |
|---|---|---|
| [logger.config.ts](file:///d:/1_Hoc_Tap/1_1_Dai_Hoc/Tai_lieu_ki_2_nam_3/T2_Kien_truc_phan_mem/Do-an-flashcard/FlashCardBackend/Flash_Learn_BE/src/config/logger.config.ts) | Central logging configuration | Exports a single `winstonConfig` object reused in both `main.ts` and `app.module.ts` |
| [main.ts](file:///d:/1_Hoc_Tap/1_1_Dai_Hoc/Tai_lieu_ki_2_nam_3/T2_Kien_truc_phan_mem/Do-an-flashcard/FlashCardBackend/Flash_Learn_BE/src/main.ts) | App entry point | Logger created *before* `NestFactory.create()` to catch bootstrap errors |
| [app.module.ts](file:///d:/1_Hoc_Tap/1_1_Dai_Hoc/Tai_lieu_ki_2_nam_3/T2_Kien_truc_phan_mem/Do-an-flashcard/FlashCardBackend/Flash_Learn_BE/src/app.module.ts) | Root module | `WinstonModule.forRoot()` enables DI across all modules |
| [requestLog.interceptor.ts](file:///d:/1_Hoc_Tap/1_1_Dai_Hoc/Tai_lieu_ki_2_nam_3/T2_Kien_truc_phan_mem/Do-an-flashcard/FlashCardBackend/Flash_Learn_BE/src/middleware/interceptor/requestLog.interceptor.ts) | HTTP request/response logger | Uses `response.on('finish')` to measure actual duration |
| [global.filter.ts](file:///d:/1_Hoc_Tap/1_1_Dai_Hoc/Tai_lieu_ki_2_nam_3/T2_Kien_truc_phan_mem/Do-an-flashcard/FlashCardBackend/Flash_Learn_BE/src/middleware/filters/global.filter.ts) | Centralized error handler | Separates internal logging from client-facing responses |
| [health.module.ts](file:///d:/1_Hoc_Tap/1_1_Dai_Hoc/Tai_lieu_ki_2_nam_3/T2_Kien_truc_phan_mem/Do-an-flashcard/FlashCardBackend/Flash_Learn_BE/src/modules/health.module.ts) | Health check wiring | Imports `TerminusModule` + `PrismaModule` |
| [health.controller.ts](file:///d:/1_Hoc_Tap/1_1_Dai_Hoc/Tai_lieu_ki_2_nam_3/T2_Kien_truc_phan_mem/Do-an-flashcard/FlashCardBackend/Flash_Learn_BE/src/controllers/health/health.controller.ts) | Health endpoints | Public endpoints (no auth) for monitoring tools |
| [prisma.health.ts](file:///d:/1_Hoc_Tap/1_1_Dai_Hoc/Tai_lieu_ki_2_nam_3/T2_Kien_truc_phan_mem/Do-an-flashcard/FlashCardBackend/Flash_Learn_BE/src/services/health/prisma.health.ts) | Database health indicator | `SELECT 1` — cheapest possible DB verification |

